## 🔀 Git Workflow

```bash
# ── See what changed ────────────────────────────────────────────
git status

# ── Stage everything ────────────────────────────────────────────
git add .

# ── Review staged changes ───────────────────────────────────────
git diff --staged

# ── Commit (Conventional Commits format) ───────────────────────
git commit -m "feat(firmware): scaffold project and add ESP32 heartbeat simulation

- Add PlatformIO config targeting ESP32 DevKit v1
- Add config.h with centralized pin and timing constants
- Implement heartbeat LED pattern with Serial diagnostics
- Add Wokwi diagram.json and wokwi.toml for browser simulation
- Scaffold backend/ and ml/ directories for future milestones
- Add docs/architecture.md with system overview
- Update README.md with Wokwi simulation badge and milestone table"

# ── Push ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
git push origin main